comments.author: achow101
comments.body: This is a known issue with using external drives with Bitcoin Core on MacOS 13.0. See https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/26455 for some more information.It looks to be an operating system bug and it seems to be resolved by upgrading to the 13.1 beta or downgrading to 12.x. At this time, there is no fix in Bitcoin Core for this issue, nor a workaround other than downgrading or upgrading your version of MacOS.
